name: MetaCat
introduce: MetaCat is a Metaverse Data Analytics & Content Navigation platform. Providing vast amount of data from major metaverses, such as Otherside, The Sandbox, Decentraland, NFT Worlds, Worldwide Webb, Voxels, Somnium Space, Netvrk. From overview of the various metaverses, heatmap analytics to monthly reports, MetaCat is committed to empower data analytics and content navigation to the metacverse ecosystem. In addition, MetaCat and two other institutions jointly established WearableDao, dedicated to the new business form of digital goods in the metaverse.
